What would happen if I fire and forget a task like that :

HostingEnvironment.QueueBackgroundWorkItem(async cancellationToken =>  
{  
 await CallWebServerAsync();  
});

Will it release the thread used by QueueBackgroundWorkItem while calling the web server so the thread can serve other requests? With a web application in .Net

